You are punished for multiple crimes.

289
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,400
Men,

290
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,280
throw Wang Ke into prison,

291
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,880
to be executed after autumn.

292
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:53,800
As for his family,

293
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,400
the men will be exiled,

294
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,860
and the women sent to the Jiaofang Division.

295
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,640
Lord Wang,

296
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,800
if you don't want to leave with dignity,

297
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:08,130
I can help you with that.

298
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,440
Anyone who dares to plead for him

299
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,960
will be considered an accomplice

300
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,240
and punished equally.

301
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,760
Yes.

302
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,480
In this novel,

303
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,560
Daqian is a deeply corrupt dynasty.

304
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,920
Su Ningxue is tyrannical and despotic.

305
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,520
To change the fate of certain death,

306
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:42,050
the court's discipline must be revitalized.

307
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,960
This is so hard for me.

308
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,440
Lord Lin.

309
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,440
How are things?

310
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,240
Have you been well these days?

311
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:00,840
I didn't expect

312
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,080
you to be the Deputy Minister of the Dali Court.

313
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,480
Status is not important.

314
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,840
Serving the world

315
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,480
is what matters most.

316
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,160
Yes.

317
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,040
I read some of the files.

318
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:11,280
The cases are truly appalling.

319
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,600
The Dali Court

320
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,440
indeed has a heavy responsibility.

321
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,240
The Dali Court

322
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,120
was established by the Empress.

323
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:19,040
Do you still think the Empress is incompetent and tyrannical?

324
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,720
Merely establishing the Dali Court

325
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,120
doesn't prove anything.

326
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:23,600
I know.

327
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:26,120
Because of what happened in Luoxian Town,

328
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,680
you resent the Empress.

329
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,520
She actually has her own difficulties.

330
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,980
Actually, I know all this.

331
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,120
Daqian

332
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,040
is still being coveted by Beijing.

333
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:36,040
Internally, noble clans are in power,

334
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,280
and powerful ministers dictate.

335
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,920
Her decrees don't even leave Taiji Palace.

336
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:40,760
The Empress has barely been on the throne for two years.

337
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:42,820
She is completely stripped of power.

338
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,280
I didn't expect

339
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:45,810
you to see through all this.

340
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:47,680
So what?

341
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,560
No matter how they fight,

342
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:51,280
the commoners are the ones who suffer.

343
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,200
This empire belongs to her.

344
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,890
If she can't solve it...

345
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,200
Who else can solve it?

346
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,610
Who says it can't be solved?

347
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:04,800
Be prepared.

348
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,040
Reform

349
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:07,640
usually comes with bloodshed

350
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:08,520
and sacrifice.

